1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a clustering algorithm for antecedent parameter estimation in TSK fuzzy classifiers, which is a common machine learning technique. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): TSK fuzzy classifiers are a type of AI model, and the paper proposes an algorithm to improve their performance. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The SESSC algorithm can be used for image clustering and classification tasks, which are common in computer vision. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The SESSC algorithm can also be applied to text data for clustering and classification tasks, which are common in natural language processing. 
5. cs.DM (Data Mining): The paper proposes a clustering algorithm that considers both within-cluster compactness, between-cluster separation, and label information, which are important aspects of data mining.
